<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ fạdy ạlạ̹nsạn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - yạ fạdy ạlạ̹nsạn yạ mnqdẖ ạlbsẖr
 kẖlṣnạ yạ rḥmạn bạlḥb wạlgẖfrạn
 1- ʿrfnạ ạlmḥbh bbdẖl nfsk fy sbylnạ
 ʿlmnạ ạ̉n nbdẖl nfwsnạ fy sbyl ạ̹kẖwạtnạ
 2- ạ̹dẖạ kạn ạllh qd ạ̉ḥbnạ hdẖạ ạlḥb
 fʿlynạ nḥn ạ̉n yḥb bʿḍnạ bʿḍạaⁿ</lyrics>
<hymn_number>7195</hymn_number>
</song>